Package: libarqma
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: ArQmA libraries
 This package contains the common arqma library code used by the other arqma
 packages.

Package: arqmad
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: arqma-blockchain-utils
Description: ArQmA node
 This package contains the arqma P2P node, arqmad, for synchronizing and
 supporting the ArQmA blockchain.

Package: arqma-wallet
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: arqmad
Description: ArQmA command-line and RPC wallets
 This package contains the arqma command-line and RPC interfaces to access a
 wallet on the ArQmA blockchain.
 .
 arqma-wallet-cli is a command-line interface to an ArQmA wallet.
 .
 arqma-wallet-rpc provides a JSON RPC interface to an ArQmA wallet and is
 typically used by software such as pools that need to interact with a wallet.
 .
 Both wallets requires an arqma node to work, such as the provided in the
 arqmad package.

Package: arqma-blockchain-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: arqmad, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: ArQmA blockchain utilities
 This contains the arqma-blockchain-* binaries for blockchain export/import and
 analysis.
